  "instructions": [
    "heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add garlic and ginger and sauté until fragrant.",
    "add sliced plantains and cook until they start to caramelize.",
    "add tamarind paste, cumin, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "deglaze the pan with lime juice, scraping up any browned bits.",
    "cook for an additional 2 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "garnish with chopped cilantro, if desired.",
    "serve immediately.",
    "enjoy!"
